      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This unit boasts crisp throttle response via its individual throttle bodies and a properly functioning double-VANOS system. Power is managed through a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a torque-sensing limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a documented rear subframe reinforcement and rod bearing replacement. The suspension has been upgraded with a Bilstein PSS10 coilover kit for improved damping and cornering kinematics. While the exterior shows minor stone chips and patina consistent with spirited use, the chassis remains rigid and the powertrain delivers linear, aspirated performance up to its 8,000 RPM redline.",
